4 CONC ary: ZENOBIA S. MULLER Born Gralewo, Poland June 18, 1925 - February 17, 2011 Zenobia Muller, beloved mother, grandmother, and great-grandmother, passed away at the age of 85 years at Concordia Hospit
4 CONC al. She is survived by; her daughter Eva, sons Richard (Tina) and Ted (Tracy), four grandchildren , and one great-granddaughter. She leaves to mourn her two sisters and their families in Poland. She w
4 CONC as predeceased by her husband John and her daughter Annette Muller. The family would like to thank Concordia nurses and assistants on third floor east for her care. Funeral services will be held on Sa
4 CONC turday, February 26, 2011 at 10:00 a.m. at St. Alphonsus Parish, Munroe Ave. and Brazier St., Winnipeg with Father Janusz Maron officiating. In keeping with Zenobia&#039;s wishes, cremation has taken 
4 CONC place and interment will be held at a later date. Mom, your unconditional love and support will remain in our hearts forever. CROPO FUNERAL CHAPEL 586-8044 Published on February 19, 2011&amp;lt;br&amp
