3 TEXT Brett A.J. Aresco&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Birth: Mar 13 1986&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Death: Oct 7 2017&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;Obituary text: Brett A.J. Aresco, age 31, of West Haven passed away suddenly at home on Octobe
4 CONC r 7, 2017. Born in New haven, son of Ronald (Donna Wilbur) Aresco and Lorraine Barquin Aresco all of West Haven. He is also survived by his brother Jesse Aresco of West Haven, his fraternal grandmothe
4 CONC r Janet Aresco of West Haven and his maternal grandmother Carol Barquin of CA, his aunt Lori Carlson of West Haven, his uncle Wayne (Patty) Aresco of Litchfield, James (Lisa) Barquin of CA, Joseph Bar
4 CONC quin of Hamden and John (Kerry) Barquin of Stratford, his cousins Matthew Carlson, Ryan, James, Anthony, Briana and Tyler Barquin. He was predeceased by his fraternal grandfather Alfred Aresco and his
4 CONC  maternal grandfather James Barquin. Brett was employed as a reservation agent with CT Limo. He was avid fisherman and loved to watch his Boston Bruins and Red Sox. The hours for visitation will be We
4 CONC dnesday from 4-7pm at the West Haven Funeral Home at the Green.
